Package: mcbrnet
Type: Package
Title: Simulation functions for metacommunity dynamics in a branching network
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Akira Terui
Maintainer: Akira Terui <hanabi0111@gmail.com>
Description: Simulation functions for metacommunity dynamics in a brancing network.
    A function \code{brnet} generates a random branching network and returns adjacency and distance matrices.
    A function \code{mcsim} simulates metacommunity dynamics. By default, it produces a square-shaped landscape with randomly distributed habitat patches. Matrices generated by \code{brnet} may be used to simulate metacommunity dynamics in a branching network.
